{"tid":1852992,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【不聽民意封關禁內地人湧港】 Ben Sir寸林鄭:其情感禁區可能已經封關","createTime":"2020-01-30T17:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T03:11:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b045ca96cfc2b8ffde3a4d111921e884d5fd7024","tid":1852992,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_722207_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_722207_0&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=48628e93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_722207_0&h=4339a9ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_722207_0</a><br />\n<br />\n【不聽民意封關禁內地人湧港】 Ben Sir寸林鄭:其情感禁區可能已經封關<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200130/1536pix/1580376777_5cbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200130%2F1536pix%2F1580376777_5cbb.jpg&h=48487659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n網上流傳，武漢肺炎三分天災，七分人禍。內地隱瞞疫情致一發不可收拾，累及全世界。港人面對港府不聽民意，遲遲唔肯完全封關，亦民怨暴升，事關特首還振振有詞說:「百分之七十以上通過這些口岸管制站的人士，無論是出或入，都是香港居民，我們為甚麼要全封這些關，令香港居民不能出，不能入？」，但民意所指的封關，是禁止非本地居民的內地人湧港，因此某些學者指她在偷換概念，而Ben Sir喺呢個討論上，都出擊喇！<br />\n<br />\n「特首質疑封關是否禁止香港居民的進出，採用了(1&rdquo;)阻止任何人出與入&rdquo;的理解:任何人包括香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n可是，我們徠來都不是指限制港人進入，因為採用(2)&rdquo;限制某些人出與入&rdquo;的理解，某些人包括內地人，不包括香港人。<br />\n<br />\n特首把大眾的概念(2)換成概念(1)，還強調了兩次，不是偷換，而是明換概念了。<br />\n<br />\n直至今天，仍然未全面封關(概念2)，完全不聽民意不顧及市民感受，其情感的禁區可能已經封關了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200130/1536pix/1580376361_a1eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200130%2F1536pix%2F1580376361_a1eb.jpg&h=ee39b88b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200130/1536pix/1580376363_e8fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200130%2F1536pix%2F1580376363_e8fd.jpg&h=3d4b60ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------"},{"pid":"81fb8139bfe9a0bd3d61484d5eb62477ca72380c","tid":1852992,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"擸一擸以為係郭富城"},{"pid":"d3addf1a117ed7e0908346ba1bf32519ab50b607","tid":1852992,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:18:02.000Z","msg":"個頭咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785c84b1661275061d83fdff58cf76c62f4840b8","tid":1852992,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b045ca96cfc2b8ffde3a4d111921e884d5fd7024","tid":1852992,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_722207_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_722207_0&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=48628e93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_722207_0&h=4339a9ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_722207_0</a><br />\n<br />\n【不聽民意封關禁內地人湧港】 Ben Sir寸林鄭:其情感禁區可能已經封關<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200130/1536pix/1580376777_5cbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200130%2F1536pix%2F1580376777_5cbb.jpg&h=48487659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n網上流傳，武漢肺炎三分天災，七分人禍。內地隱瞞疫情致一發不可收拾，累及全世界。港人面對港府不聽民意，遲遲唔肯完全封關，亦民怨暴升，事關特首還振振有詞說:「百分之七十以上通過這些口岸管制站的人士，無論是出或入，都是香港居民，我們為甚麼要全封這些關，令香港居民不能出，不能入？」，但民意所指的封關，是禁止非本地居民的內地人湧港，因此某些學者指她在偷換概念，而Ben Sir喺呢個討論上，都出擊喇！<br />\n<br />\n「特首質疑封關是否禁止香港居民的進出，採用了(1&rdquo;)阻止任何人出與入&rdquo;的理解:任何人包括香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n可是，我們徠來都不是指限制港人進入，因為採用(2)&rdquo;限制某些人出與入&rdquo;的理解，某些人包括內地人，不包括香港人。<br />\n<br />\n特首把大眾的概念(2)換成概念(1)，還強調了兩次，不是偷換，而是明換概念了。<br />\n<br />\n直至今天，仍然未全面封關(概念2)，完全不聽民意不顧及市民感受，其情感的禁區可能已經封關了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200130/1536pix/1580376361_a1eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200130%2F1536pix%2F1580376361_a1eb.jpg&h=ee39b88b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200130/1536pix/1580376363_e8fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200130%2F1536pix%2F1580376363_e8fd.jpg&h=3d4b60ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7792481a22e48d53f5c569bf6281f1a35ebce71e","tid":1852992,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:45:04.000Z","msg":"一切掉進廢墟"},{"pid":"ac2df68d92264861f201f322946b146a396f0c14","tid":1852992,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一切掉進禁區</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f66b984eff142b968cc5885b69c2810fa4d6743a","tid":1852992,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T03:12:09.000Z","msg":"髮型禁區"},{"pid":"68b39b01dff1048bad0c543deaf6688884cb663e","tid":1852992,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"「特首質疑封關是否禁止香港居民的進出，採用了(1&rdquo;)阻止任何人出與入&rdquo;的理解:任何人包括香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n可是，我們徠來都不是指限制港人進入，因為採用(2)&rdquo;限制某些人出與入&rdquo;的理解，某些人包括內地人，不包括香港人。<br />\n<br />\n特首把大眾的概念(2)換成概念(1)，還強調了兩次，不是偷換，而是明換概念了。<br />\n<br />\n直至今天，仍然未全面封關(概念2)，完全不聽民意不顧及市民感受，其情感的禁區可能已經封關了。」"},{"pid":"78a4f8194c63bed26415ab72aee0205c6163103e","tid":1852992,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:10:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家幫手推一推，正個評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-si